    <body>
        <h1>Welcome to Sound 56's website!</h1>
		<p>The Sound 56 website is a platform for sharing musical compositions, whatever they are. It is a kind of social network for music lovers wishing to support composers or share their own compositions.<br><br>
		
        <p>This site will allow you to consult profiles of music addicts from all over the world! Of course you don't have to create an account. You can go directly to the "profile's feed" page to consult all the profiles created on this platform.But if you want to share your musical productions, you will have to create an account beforehand.</p>
        <h2>It's up to you now!</h2><br>
        <div id="valeurs">
            <h1>What can you do?</h1>
                <div class="conteneur">
                    <div class="element1"><img src="/public/images/createProfile.png" alt="profile icon"> 
                        <p><strong>Create a profile</strong></p></div>
                    <div class="element2"><img src="/public/images/browsing.png" alt="browsing icon">
                        <p><strong>Browse other profiles</strong></p></div>
                    <div class="element3"><img src="/public/images/listeningMusic.png" alt="music icon">
                        <p><strong>Share musical compositions</strong></p></div> 
                </div>
        </div><br><br>

        <p>If you don't have a profile yet, create one now by clicking on the button below!</p>

        <div class="centerButton">
           <button onclick="location.href = '/createProfile'" name="createProfile" class="button" >Create a profile</button>
        </div><br><br><br>
    </body>

